dc_title_s: National Boundary, Turks and Caicos Islands, 2015
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains the national boundary of Turks and Caicos Islands (adm0). This layer is part of the Global Administrative Areas 2015 (v2.8) dataset. Hijmans, R. and University of California, Berkeley, Museum of Vertebrate Zoology. (2015). National Boundary, Turks and Caicos Islands, 2015. UC Berkeley, Museum of Vertebrate Zoology. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/dr464zk4328 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
